  "text": "There are other research studies focusing on performance measurements and tests of UASs using IEEE 802.11 as the communication network. The channel fading properties through spatial diversity, by employing multiple antennas are studied in [CITATION_1] . The final scheme includes a small, low-altitude UAV within an 802.11 wireless mesh network.",
